{
  "stem": "3475.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Also, many Jews from Poland-- from Poland did work as craftsmen and did work as-- they had-- they were oriented into the physical work more than the Jews from Italy or Holland or Belgium, or other fields like that.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The Jews from Belgium did speak Yiddish, most of them, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because I guess their ancestors came from Eastern Europe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you asked me what we were wearing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK, here's, here's something good to bring up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were wearing-- summer and winter, it was just a, a blouse, you know, a striped blouse.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't if it was cotton, or ersatz-- artificial cotton, I don't know, and, and pants, and underwear, you know, sort of underwear.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- which in the summertime wasn't too bad, when it was hot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in wintertime, when we had to work, it was freezing cold.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the wintertime, as I remember, they did give us a little cotton overcoat, which also wasn't very warm.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had a hat, a round hat, with the stripes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so what we were doing, we were taking-- we had contact with cement because we had to load cement where-- railroad cars and unload cement-- railroad cars with cement.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we used to take the empty bags from cement.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I used to cut out-- we used to cut out holes for the arms and for the neck.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we would slip it-- shake it out good and slip it under our clothing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And also, I would take the cement-- the bag-- and cut it out in strips and wrap up our legs and our torso, you know, to keep the wind out.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It helped a lot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it insulated us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the Germans were against it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
